This is a customized version of Live2D Live Wallpaper for Android

Features:
Custom background with gyroscope function, character also have gyroscope function too.
Easy to edit!
Lightweight size, no assets inside!

Requirement:
Android Studio to use the source code!

Source:
Live2D Cubism SDK: http://www.live2d.com/en/download
